name: Evolve Artificial Intelligence Fund
longDescription: ARTI collaborates with Boosted.ai to utilize their state-of-the-art generative AI platform and proprietary scoring to strategically select companies set to benefit significantly from AI integration in the years ahead.
fulldescription: ARTI collaborates with Boosted.ai to utilize their state-of-the-art generative AI platform and proprietary scoring to strategically select companies set to benefit significantly from AI integration in the years ahead. The investment objective of the Evolve Fund is to provide exposure to securities of publicly traded issuers that the Manager has determined are expected to benefit from increased adoption of AI.
